title: Play-Doh Super Colour Pack, Non-Toxic Modelling Compound Set with 20 Colours for Toddlers, Creative Toys for 2+ Year Old Kids, Arts and Crafts
features: VIBRANT COLOUR COLLECTION: 20 bright Play-Doh colours for 2+ year old boys and girls provides limitless opportunities for artistic expression and imaginative creations
VERSATILE CREATION TOOLS: Equipped with various moulds and shapes, enabling kids to imagine, easily cut, stamp, and sculpt their favourite designs with Play-Doh modelling clay
ENTERTAINMENT FOR THE YOUNGEST: 2+ year old children can enjoy fun activities with friends using this Play-Doh playset of arts and crafts toys
EASY TO STORE AND USE: Organised in a convenient setup, ensuring all 20 Play-Doh 85-g cans and accessories are neatly stored and ready for creative play anytime, anywhere
QUALITY YOU TRUST: Play-Doh has been a favourite since 1956! Made with water, salt, and flour, the non-toxic arts and crafts modelling clay toy undergoes rigorous testing to ensure its quality
description: From the manufacturer Play-Doh compound is a non-toxic compound designed to be used again and again. It is a mixture of water, salt and flour and is not manufactured in a faculty that manufactures food. It is not intended to be eaten and can be harmful to pets if ingested due to high salt content. Play-Doh Super Colour This big pack of 20 cans of Play-Doh modeling compound holds an endless array of creative possibilities! Little hands can roll, twist and shape these colors into any form that strikes their fancies, then mash them up and start all over. Perfect for play dates and parties, the Super Color Pack is just the ticket for big Play-Doh fun!
